div.head:
Memorandum by the Ambassador in the United Kingdom
    (
    Aldrich
) to the British Secretary of State for Foreign
    Affairs (
    Eden
)Memorandum sent to Eden in accordance with instructions
    contained in telegram 5090 to London, Apr. 1; for text, see volume xiii
    . Copy transmitted to the Department as enclosure to despatch 3357
    from London, Apr. 6, not printed. (396.1 GE/4–654)
